    "In the UPGRADE mode, the solution is better if it does not violate O1 and has higher accuracy.",
    "Here, we define accuracy as the weighted average of all clients' inference accuracy (determined by the DNN's profiled accuracy to which it is mapped, otherwise zero), where the clients' frame rate determines the weight (see Eq.",
